title: Red Book
author: wolf359
pages:
#- Red Book of Passion
#- I want you. In every meaning of the word, even the ones you can't think of.
   My heart takes a leap at the sight of you and your voice sends shivers down my spine.
   I'd be crazy about you no matter what. It's about who you are who I am and
#- what we are together. How you make me feel and think.

And I want you to know that I've always gotten whoever I've wanted. You don't need to do anything, I've already got you.
#- 